                        <interp inst="t18490129-name-888" type="given" value="WILLIAM THOMAS"></interp>WILLIAM THOMAS BRIDGES</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Thames police-inspector</hi>). I produce a cer<lb></lb>tificate of the prisoner's conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted April</hi>, 1848, <hi rend="italic">confined six months</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
